    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607864187825160759&sectionId=607888589312754262)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeP0XsBuiO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggeP0XsBuiO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-adca4081-72c8-4390-b0c6-6193971e572f.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gguls-ItZR8_text","label":"gguls-ItZR8_text","default":"<p>This explained everything. The drugs my doctor wanted to prescribe would never actually rebuild my bones.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv_zir-gt__text","label":"ggv_zir-gt__text","default":"<p>They'd just trap them in a state of suspended decay.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFuZBzz2hs_text","label":"ggFuZBzz2hs_text","default":"<p><strong>That's When Dr. Chen Revealed The Real solution.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjYx5-9pbs_text","label":"ggjYx5-9pbs_text","default":"<p>He explained that NAD+ doesn't work alone. You need three things working together: NAD+, Resveratrol &amp; Quercetin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoCXfAjMCa_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggoCXfAjMCa_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1ac8eee2-7a94-4b1d-aada-093f8c512a9d.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCDnVLNrFf_text","label":"ggCDnVLNrFf_text","default":"<p><strong>Together, these 3 ingredients create a complete system:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaX0UIHvZk_text","label":"ggaX0UIHvZk_text","default":"<p>1. Restores energy to the osteoblasts.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR7SuXt7md_text","label":"ggR7SuXt7md_text","default":"<p>2. Activate the bone-builders.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwv586UOXX_text","label":"ggwv586UOXX_text","default":"<p>3. Calms the osteoclasts.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKG3kzicrQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggKG3kzicrQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_c7gbbvc7gbbvc7gb_ddba5816-e417-4342-b9e5-2f3279b045a5.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw2b4bwXal_text","label":"ggw2b4bwXal_text","default":"<p><strong>Dr. Chen's Personal Crisis: The Reason He Left Big Pharma</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz4N5O3-TB_text","label":"ggz4N5O3-TB_text","default":"<p>Dr. Chen's mother had no symptoms.</p><p>She felt fine. She thought she was healthy.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5IwIIyyke_text","label":"gg5IwIIyyke_text","default":"<p>That was the terrifying part. Then one day, while visiting family, she stepped off a curb.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1diAmsMHb_text","label":"gg1diAmsMHb_text","default":"<p>Just a simple step down. Her ankle shattered.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfBRLcFa5W_text","label":"ggfBRLcFa5W_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"Not a bad sprain. Not a minor fracture... A complete break from what should have been nothing.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggW_gXkr0NI_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggW_gXkr0NI_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/applsci-11-08791-g001.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyve-F6dTL_text","label":"ggyve-F6dTL_text","default":"<p><strong>She was devastated. Debilitating. Depressing. Dr. Chen watched his mother's world collapse overnight.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTSCzGlqMG_text","label":"ggTSCzGlqMG_text","default":"<p>Suddenly she couldn't walk without pain. Couldn't do the things that made her feel like herself. Her independence vanished in a single moment.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfHVVw0ftD_text","label":"ggfHVVw0ftD_text","default":"<p>And the worst part?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyJK5eVZmv_text","label":"ggyJK5eVZmv_text","default":"<p>Her rheumatologist still had no real answers. He prescribed Fosamax and told her to take more calcium.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGZSsPpcaW_text","label":"ggGZSsPpcaW_text","default":"<p><strong>Dr. Chen became furious.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYmzIMNmMH_text","label":"ggYmzIMNmMH_text","default":"<p>Not at his mother. At a system that let this happen. A system that called it \"silent disease\" and then acted shocked when women broke bones from everyday life.</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
